ActNational Capital Act
SubjectOrder Approving that National Capital Commission Extend the Easement with Hydro One Networks Inc.
PrecisOrder approving that National Capital Commission grant an extension of an existing easement to HYDRO ONE NETWORKS INC. for a period of 29 years, 9 months and 27 days, beginning on August 20, 2062, for the real property located in Ottawa, Ontario.
